TXC CORP (3042)  said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 0.62% to NT$765,504,000 from NT$770,267,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            765,504          770,267    
YOY%              -0.62%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,866,237        2,852,053   
YOY%              0.50%  
=================================================================
 